m. kumaran s/o mahalakshmi is a 2004 tamil family-drama film directed by m. raja , starring jayam ravi , asin &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; , prakash raj , nadhiya in the lead roles while vivek , &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; and janagaraj play supporting roles . the film 's score and soundtrack are composed by srikanth deva . it is a remake of super hit telugu film amma nanna o &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ammayi starring ravi teja , asin , prakash raj , jayasudha , &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; , aishwarya sivachandran , and ali , directed by puri jagannadh which was released on 19 april 2003 .